% a given pattern. 

% a pattern is defined from a used defined ROI in a given field of view

% arguments :
% fovid: id of the field of view in which a user defined ROI is present
% roiid: id of the roiid in which the defined is roi is present
% frameid: etc...
% channel id: etc...

if nargin<=3
    frameid=1;
    channelid=1;
end

